org.eclipse.keyple.transaction

Class SeSelectionRequest

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.keyple.transaction.SeSelectionRequest

  • public class SeSelectionRequest
extends java.lang.Object
    The SeSelectionRequest class combines a SeSelector with additional helper methods useful to the selection process done in SeSelection.

    This class may also be extended to add particular features specific to a SE family.

      • addApduRequest

        protected final void addApduRequest(ApduRequest apduRequest)
        Add an additional ApduRequest to be executed after the selection process if it succeeds.

        If more than one ApduRequest is added, all will be executed in the order in which they were added.

        Parameters:
        apduRequest - an ApduRequest
